<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Welcome to the Flowra Framework – a clean, scalable, and beautiful Node.js foundation for modern developers."
    />
    <title>Welcome to Flowra Framework</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/welcome.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-shell">
      <div class="background-wave" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <header class="page-header">
        <div class="brand-and-nav">
          <div class="brand">
            <div class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
              <img
                src="/imgs/flowra.png"
                alt="Flowra Logo"
                class="brand-logo"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="brand-name" aria-label="flowra">flowra</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <nav class="meta">
          <span class="meta-item">
            <span class="label">Environment</span>
            <span class="value"><%= metadata.environment %></span>
          </span>
          <span class="meta-divider" role="presentation">•</span>
          <span class="meta-item">
            <span class="label">Node.js</span>
            <span class="value"><%= metadata.nodeVersion %></span>
          </span>
          <span class="meta-divider" role="presentation">•</span>
          <span class="meta-item">
            <span class="label">Uptime</span>
            <span class="value"><%= metadata.uptime %></span>
          </span>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main class="hero" role="main">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <p class="tagline">Flow with clarity</p>
          <h1>Welcome to Flowra Framework</h1>
          <p class="subheadline">
            A Clean, Scalable, and Beautiful Node.js Framework for Modern Developers.
          </p>
          <p class="philosophy">
            Flowra is inspired by the effortless movement of water (mili). We believe in flow, clarity, and
            maintainability principles that let your ideas travel smoothly from concept to deployment with
            confidence and grace.
          </p>
          <div class="quick-links" aria-label="Quick start links">
            <a
              class="quick-link"
              href="<%= githubLink %>"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              GitHub Repo
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="feature-card" aria-label="Framework highlights">
          <h2>Why Flowra?</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Elegant foundations:</strong> Opinionated patterns keep your architecture calm and confident.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Scalable core:</strong> Modular design lets your application grow organically without friction.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Developer experience:</strong> Thoughtful tooling so you can focus on delivering value.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </main>

      <footer class="page-footer">
        <p>© <%= currentYear %> Flowra Core Team. Crafted for builders.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
